metadata.name: SILENT
metadata.description:
'SILENT' is a Surreal Landscape art from an exoplanet. It is the third artwork in the series of my "TRAQUIL" creations featuring smooth modern minimal landscapes with a surreal vibe to it. The title of this artwork 'SILENT' signifies the calm and peaceful nature of the planet.

MEDIUM: Digital 3d Art || YEAR: 2022 || DIMENSIONS: 4000*5000px(base x height) || DEPTH: 600ppi (48-bit) || COLOR SCHEME: sRGB
